The,Elorus,Developers,API,allows,developers,to,programmatically,access,the,Elorus,invoicing,and,billing,platform,as,well,as,update,organization,data,This,API,can,be,used,to,connect,with,a,small,business,e,shop,or,website,in,order,to,automate,invoice,processing,and,synchronize,data,Elorus,can,handle,multiple,user,accounts,and,multiple,currencies